milestones.description: Craig White and Paul Collingwood's 110-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 86 between Mike Gatting and Paul Downton

stories.title: Collingwood ton helps England reach 258
stories.summary: PERTH, Dec 20 AAP - Paul Collingwood's maiden one-day international century guided England to 9-258 off 50 overs in its day-night cricket match against Sri Lanka at the WACA Ground.

stories.title: England triumph again as Sri Lanka subside
stories.summary: England completed their second successive victory in the VB triangular series, beating a lacklustre Sri Lanka by 95 runs at the WACA

stories.title: Hussain wins toss and bats against Sri Lanka
stories.summary: PERTH, Dec 20 AAP - England captain Nasser Hussain won the toss and elected to bat in the day-night cricket match against Sri Lanka at the WACA Ground today.
